node.text:
Sit back and enjoy @_morenob and @jon1of1 in a new edit by @kevperez - the boys skating Los Angeles in the all new éS Cykle. Out now on esskateboarding.com
Full video now live on our YouTube channel - link in bio.

The CYKLE has an inner sock that wraps around the ankle keeping the foot snug to enhance stability and control while keeping the outer shell loose and fresh AF. The upper has breathable STI Everstitch mesh, STI Thermothane for lightweight Duraflex, and the unique webbing strap system allows the skater to tighten or loosen upwards tension depending on individual preference. The unique highly durable rubber outsole has been tested for perfect board feel and supreme comfort unlike any other skate shoe available. If you’re ready to perform to your highest level, and look better than ever, the éS CYKLE is for you. 
#eS_CYKLE
